g.text: Routes to include in the project:
GET /api/users - to select an existing user to "log in"
GET /api/articles - displays a list of all articles (In Newsfeed, drop down list for queries: "sort_by","order", "topic")
GET /api/articles/:article_id - display the article that got clicked on
GET /api/articles/:article_id/comments - displays the comments underneath that article/post
(show the number of comments before clicking to display all)
POST /api/articles/:article_id/comments - be able to directly add a comment underneath the other comments on
DELETE /api/comments/:comment_id - be able to delete a comment (if the comment id matches the user id).
PATCH /api/articles/:article_id - used to increment or decrement votes of that specific article
search for a topic or title...
searchbar is within ArticleCard (for filtering by topics, title, or author)
be able to scroll through all articles
drop down list to sort by:
be able to scroll through all comments
be able to scroll through all articles associated
